  "title": "Electrician cum aircon installer",
  "description": "<p><strong>Company Overview / Employee Value Proposition</strong></p><p>STL ELECTRICAL CONTRACTOR is looking for an electrician in Singapore to work at construction sites.</p><p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><p>You will perform electrical wiring and air conditioning installation at construction sites while following instructions from the foreman and ensuring compliance with electrical codes.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Perform electrical wiring installation at construction sites to meet project specifications and safety standards</li><li>Install air conditioning systems at construction sites according to technical requirements and manufacturer guidelines</li><li>Follow instructions from the foreman accurately to support project progress and quality</li><li>Apply knowledge of electrical codes to ensure all electrical work complies with regulatory and safety standards</li></ul>",
